channel.title: No one can get on my server!
channel.description: Before we start i am not going to say the usual 127.0.0.1 NO! i have tryed Ham and No-ip both do not work. I had them workin yesterday. Every time someone tryies to log on i think the come up as a null. What can i do? any ideas please[br][size=1]Posted on: January 11, 2007, 06:50:53 PM[/size][hr]Fixed the prob now, i forgot to change my port forwarding address :P
